quran[5]{c,v,t}:
  111,1,"Abii lahab namma gaba finqiteh, kaadu usuk finqiteh."
  111,2,"Kay maaluy yedderee kee kay xaylo Kaah xiqtem maliiy yallih digaalak tu kaak ma çatta."
  111,3,"Usuk Кахха ura-le giray hadiidigta Culele."
  111,4,"Kaadu kay barray bocó takkuqih tani, girá kaâ luk culele."
  111,5,"Tet fıllat cambok yan akatay is jahannam giráh addal edde diggalsimta yan."
